                <h1>Ted Bundy: The Infamous Serial Killer</h1>
                <p>Ted Bundy was one of America's most notorious serial killers, known for his charm and intelligence which allowed him to lure victims. Operating mainly in the 1970s, he confessed to 30 homicides, though the true number may be higher. His heinous acts, trial, and eventual execution in 1989 continue to fascinate and horrify.</p>
